/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"世侄，咪話呀叔唔點醒你<br />\n其實你能夠由asso升到上u己經好叻<br />\n其實出到黎做野真係除咗第一份工<br />\n之後其實無撚人理你邊間大學畢業<br />\n三唔三大真係無撚所謂 v<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v<br />\n大撚把所謂三大人都好霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以老土講句 繼續做好自己就夠啦 加油呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"多謝叔叔鼓勵 我會嘗試樂觀啲㗎喇<br />\n但係asso升到上u嘅真係周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼見身邊grad咗嘅師兄師姐有好多都仲未揾到工<br />\n我自己都好淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a066ba6adb6584788f70a2ee1ef3d062d57531","tid":2199001,"uid":367758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"成日話乞食<br />\n而家讀5讀U都好似冇分別咁<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"a222eec92ea74dc3de110a41b5e4d359acd1a2af","tid":2199001,"uid":191425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42809108d79b70c1bb3e617327fef746db45f3f4","tid":2199001,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:02:19.000Z","msg":"入三大 同報答父母有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"自細體弱多病 成日要佢哋照顧<br />\n諗住入間好啲嘅U會令佢哋開心啲咋<br />\n又或者第時會易啲揾工<br />\n另一方面 有得入三大點會有人say no<br />\n覺得自己明明差少少就入到 好唔甘心<br />\n所以成日都放唔低"},{"pid":"faaf197627a7a06f035ef3a19e071d86923c8ff7","tid":2199001,"uid":367758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a222eec92ea74dc3de110a41b5e4d359acd1a2af","tid":2199001,"uid":191425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42809108d79b70c1bb3e617327fef746db45f3f4","tid":2199001,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:02:19.000Z","msg":"入三大 同報答父母有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /